        "title": "Tropical Cyclone Initial data",
        "description": "The Met Office tropical cyclone initial data are drawn from advisories received from tropical cyclone warning centres around the globe. The data includes storm names, identifiers, current location, intensity and wind structure. These data form the starting point for subsequent forecast guidance messages issued by the Met Office and other agencies (e.g. ECMWF).",
